high_descs: Walk to the corner to your left till you are near a desk.
Pick up a pen from the small table.
Turn around, walk straight up to leave the room, left down the corridor until the nearest entrance to the right, where you enter and turn towards shelves on your right.
Place the pen on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a pen from a small table and take it to a bottom shelf in another room.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the desk.
Pick up the pen on the right from the desk.
Turn back and walk come out of the room, then turn left and walk, then turn right and enter into the another room, then turn right towards the shelf.
Put a pen in the down rack of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a pen into the shelf.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right
Pick up pen from the desk
Turn back and take few steps and turn left and take immediate left turn to reach the back side of the shelf
anns.task_desc: Changing pen from one place to another
